Package gw.api.archiving.upgrade

Interface IArchivedEntitySet

All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<IArchivedEntity>
public interface IArchivedEntitySet extends Iterable<IArchivedEntity>
Represents a set of IArchivedEntity's for the same "old" entity type.
